* Main Window:
   Main GUI entry point. It should offer the options of:
    * Connect to a server -> ServerWindow
    * Play a local "hotseat" game -> two GameWindow

* Server Window:
   Main GUI window for server operations.
    * Create an account.
    * Open up a game.
    * Join a game.
    * Search users.
    * Add/Remove users from friend list.
    * Join chat channels.

* Write client_test
   This should test all the methods of ClientConnection.
